        "content": "<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span>\n<span class=\"bp\">|-</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">c</span><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"bp\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>I want to cut h to get two goals</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\">-- goal 1</span>\n<span class=\"bp\">|-</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\">-- goal 2</span>\n<span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span>\n<span class=\"bp\">|-</span><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">c</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>I don't like <code>have a &gt; = 0:= by ...</code> because the statement is too long</p>\n<p>Is there any tactic can help me ?</p>",
        "id": 476599696,
        "sender_full_name": "Yijun Leng",
        "timestamp": 1728819311
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>It is hard to be sure because you are not providing much context, but your initial goal looks like you wanted to prove <code>a &gt; 0 -&gt; b&gt;1 -&gt; c&gt;2</code> but instead typed <code>(a &gt;0 -&gt; b&gt;1) -&gt; c-&gt;2</code>; they are not the same, since <code>-&gt;</code>associates to the right and not to the left.</p>\n<p>As you wrote them, your goal 1 is essentially your hypothesis <code>h</code>, and proving your goal 2, together with <code>h</code>, will not by itself help in proving the initial goal.</p>\n<p>If instead you had started from the goal <code>|- a &gt; 0 -&gt; b &gt; 1 -&gt; c &gt; 2</code>, then the tactic <code>intro ha hb</code> would give you as a goal </p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">ha</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span>\n<span class=\"n\">hb</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">b</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span>\n<span class=\"bp\">|-</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">c</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Is that what you expected? (Sorry for the edits)</p>",
        "id": 476600239,
        "sender_full_name": "Philippe Duchon",
        "timestamp": 1728819883
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I think <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"449070\">@lengyijun</span> just wants</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">refine</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Implies</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">trans</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">?_</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">?_</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
